# Splitting files

Help the linker by splitting big source files into single-function units.

## Split Arduino core files

Effect on Blink.ino:

   code	 |  data|    RAM|  flash total	|split stage
   ----  |  ----|   ----|   ----	|------------
   2400	 |   245|     72|   2645	|before split
   2343	 |   245|     72|   2588	|after splitting wiring.c
   2274	 |   245|     72|   2519	|after splitting wiring_digital.c
   1692	 |   245|     72|   1937	|after splitting HardwareSerial.c
